title: Tugiyati Cindy
text: Tugiyati Cindy (born 21 July 1985) is an Indonesian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. She is currently playing for <a href="Putri%20Mataram">Putri Mataram</a> and is a member of the <a href="Indonesia%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Indonesia women's national football team</a>.
